    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Heads of the species of Spicomacrurus: A–B—Spicomacrurus dictyogadus, holotype, MNHN 2009-1455, redrawn from Iwamoto, Shao & Ho (2011), A—Lateral view, B—Dorsal view. C–D—Spicomacrurus adelscotti, WAM P.28073-004, C—Lateral view, D—Dorsal view. E–F—Spicomacrurus kuronumai, E—Lateral view, NSMT P46796, F—Dorsal view, NSMT P103488. G–H—Spicomacrurus mccoskeri, MNHN 1994-0881, G—Lateral view, H—Dorsal view." ;
