<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10086425>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Otoliths of the species of Spicomacrurus: A–B—Spicomacrurus adelscotti, WAM P.28073-004, A—Inner face, B—Ventral view. C–D—Spicomacrurus mccoskeri, MNHN 1994-0881, C—Inner face, D—Ventral view. E–G—Spicomacrurus kuronumai, E–F—NSMT P46796, E—Inner face, F—Ventral view, G—NSMT P103488, inner face." ;
